OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CMonday:FMostly dry and bright on
OL,6,FMonday with sunny spells for all. The
OL,7,Fodd isolated shower is again possible
OL,8,Fin the afternoon. Feeling hot and
OL,9,Fhumid.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:
OL,12,FRemaining dry and sunny throughout the
OL,13,Fperiod. Feeling hot by day in the
OL,14,Fstrong sunshine and increasingly warm
OL,15,Fand humid overnight.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
